race.comment: Small field after the scratchings but still looks a decent pace. THE DEPUTY (7) has been a model of consistency and looks the hardest to beat. Has been beaten in a photo the last two and gets chance to return to winning form with the light weight. HOLLYWOOD NORTH (2) is fitter for three runs back and looks ready to win. Will be on speed and looks ideally placed this line-up. FOR VALOUR (4) has been going well and carried a big weight last time in easier company. Will give a sight in the small field here. NONDISCLOSURE (8) resumes and while yet to score fresh is suited by the small field and the light weight.
